	<h3 style="font-size: 30px; text-align: center;">Place an Order</h3>
	<hr>
	<br/>

	<p>Users will be able to come to this page to place their orders.
		They will put in their name, the name and email of the recipient,
		pick a reward, and type in an amount.  They can click the "+" button
		to add another line, or hit "Place Order" to submit their order.</p>

	<br/>
	<div>
			<form id="orders">
				<div>
					<label for="fromName">Sender Email (optional): </label>
					<input type="text" id="fromName" name="fromName" value="fet@chet.net">
					
					<label for="rEmail">Recipient Email: </label>
					<input type="email" id="rEmail" name="rEmail" value="foo@bar">
					
					<input type="radio" id="Amazon" name="giftCard" value="Amazon">
					<label for="Amazon">Amazon</label>
					
					<input type="radio" id="Ebay" name="giftCard" value="Ebay">
					<label for="Ebay">Ebay</label>
					
					<input type="radio" id="Starbucks" name="giftCard" value="Starbucks">
					<label for="Starbucks">Starbucks</label>
					
					<input type="radio" id="Netflix" name="giftCard" value="Netflix" checked>
					<label for="Netflix">Netflix</label>
					
					<input type="radio" id="Target" name="giftCard" value="Target">
					<label for="Target">Target</label>
					
					<label for="Amount"> Amount: $</label>
					<input type="number" id="Amount" name ="Amount" value ="1000">
				</div>		
			</form>
			<input type="button" id="addLines" value="+">Add Lines</button><br>
			<br/>

	</div>

	<button id="placeOrder" style="width: 120px; margin-top: 5px; margin-bottom: 4px; margin-left: 620px;">Place Order</button>

	<br/>
	<div style="margin-left: 50px;">
			<table>
				<thead>
					<th>Sender Email</th>
					<th>Recipient Email</th>
					<th>GiftCard Name</th>
					<th>Quantity</th>
				</thead>
				<tbody>
					<tr>
						<td>{{sender_email}}</td>
						<td>{{recipient_email}}</td>
						<td>{{name}}</td>
						<td>{{quantity}}</td>
					</tr>
				</tbody>
			</table> 
	</div>
